org.franca.core.franca

Interface FInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FModelElement, FTypeCollection, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FInterfaceImpl

    public interface FInterface
extends FTypeCollection
    A representation of the model object 'FInterface'. This class represents a Franca interface definition. Interfaces are named and should be versioned (optional). Types defined as part of this interface can not be referenced by other FTypeCollections and FInterfaces. This type visibility differs from the types defined as part of FTypeCollections.

    The following features are supported:

    • Attributes
    • Methods
    • Broadcasts
    • Contract
    • Base
    • Managed Interfaces

    See Also:
    FrancaPackage.getFInterface()
